    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Explore more about Costco hot dogs:</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <a href="/hot-dog/calories/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">detailed calorie breakdown</a>
    <a href="/hot-dog/ingredients/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">what goes into it</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is a Costco hot dog healthy?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">It can fit a balanced diet occasionally, but sodium and saturated fat make it a poor choice for frequent daily intake.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What are Costco hot dog macros?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Typical macros are about 24g protein, 33g fat, and 46g carbs with bun.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is sodium the biggest concern?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">For most people, yes. One serving can use up a large percentage of the daily sodium limit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Where can I see exact calories with and without bun?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Use the dedicated <a href="/hot-dog/calories/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">calories breakdown</a> for side-by-side values and year comparison.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
